CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "8. The lovely group in Bella Fronte Cosmetics booth is the Modernes Social Club. Ernestine Stanley, seated third from right, and Bill Robinson, standing center, were representatives"
TitMainTitle: The Modernes Social Club, posed with representatives Ernestine Stanley, seated third from right, and Bill Robinson, standing center, in Bella Fronte Cosmetics booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
